   <!--THIS TOPIC IS PART OF THE BESR REPO, DO NOT EDIT IT WITHOUT CONSULTING WITH DATA FLOW AREA TECHWRITERS!!!-->
   <conbody>
      <note id="note_N1002D_N1002A_N10001">
                                    <p>The following steps require the privileges of <apiname>eea-besr-config</apiname> and <apiname>eea-besr-service</apiname>.</p>
                                 </note>
      <p>To start the Correlator cluster, execute the following command:</p>
      <codeblock>besr_cluster start corr</codeblock>
      <p>To stop the Correlator cluster, execute the following command:</p>
      <codeblock>besr_cluster stop corr</codeblock>
      <p>To check whether the Correlator cluster is running, execute the following command:</p>
      <codeblock>besr_cluster status corr</codeblock>
      <p>To enable and start the <ph keyref=""/> Correlator Healthcheck Service:</p>
      <codeblock>sudo /usr/bin/systemctl enable eea-health-check.service
sudo /usr/bin/systemctl start eea-health-check.service</codeblock>
      <note id="note_N10066_N1002A_N10001">
                                    <p>Start the service on a single host of the cluster only.</p>
                                 </note>
   </conbody>
</concept>